b8d66aab.formula:
\\text{Weighted geometric mean:} \\\quad \exp\left( \frac{ |n_A| \log r_A + |n_B| \log r_B + |n_X| \log r_X }{ |n_A| + |n_B| + |n_X| } \right) \\
\\text{Tolerance factor:} \\\quad t = \frac{ r_A + r_X }{ \sqrt{2} ( r_B + r_X ) } \\
\\text{Descriptor:} \\\quad p_0 \times ( \text{weighted geometric mean} )^{p_1} + p_2 \times ( t - 1 )^{3}

a7df317a.formula:

	ext{combined size} = \frac{r_A n_A + r_B n_B + r_X n_X}{|n_A| + |n_B| + |n_X| + 1} \\ 
 t = \frac{r_A + r_X}{\text{params}_0 (r_B + r_X)} \\ 
 \text{stability metric} = (\text{combined size} - t)^{\text{params}_1}

813e2eb5.formula:
S = (|nA| rA + |nB| rB + |nX| rX) / (|nA| + |nB| + |nX| + 1) 
T = (rA + rX) / (p_0 * (rB + rX) + 1) 
Descriptor = S * |T - 1|^{p_1}

d432aab4.formula:
Size mismatch term: exp(-|rA - rX| - |rB - rX|) 
Charge difference term: tan((|nA - nX| + |nB - nX|) * p_1) 
Tolerance factor term: ((rA + rX) / (sqrt(2) * (rB + rX)))^{p_2}

cd3230f6.formula:
Size-charge term: (|n_A| r_A + |n_B| r_B + |n_X| r_X)^{p_0} \quad\text{(power of combined size and charge)} 

Radii geometric mean: (r_A r_B r_X)^{1/3} 

Charge factor: (|n_A| + |n_B| + |n_X|)^{p_1} 

t: (r_A + r_X) / (\sqrt{2} (r_B + r_X)) 

Descriptor: (size-charge) * exp(-p_2 * |t - 1|) * (radii_mean)^{p_3}

f78e4834.formula:
Geometric mean: \quad \left( r_A^{|n_A|} \times r_B^{|n_B|} \times r_X^{|n_X|} \right)^{1/3} \\
Tolerance polynomial: \quad p_0 \times t + p_1 \times t^2, \quad \text{where } t = \frac{r_A + r_X}{\sqrt{2}(r_B + r_X)} \\
Descriptor: \quad \text{Geometric mean} \times \text{Tolerance polynomial}
